title: Bowling for Ballers
description: Axel and the team must intervene when Zoe's not-so-friendly bowling competition with Cleo LeBall gets interrupted by Madcap, Porcupunk, and their new cohort, the mischievously magnetic Dynamo.

title: Saving Private Masko
description: Masko takes Axel's call for more discipline too seriously and loses sight of his own identity in the process, becoming a no-nonsense soldier set on toeing the line - and ill-equipped for a lucha libre with Madcap!

title: Swing Set Jet Set
description: Axel and the team battle Princess SugarSalt for possession of Bearbarian's hammer, traded to her by one of their own - Galileo!

title: Prepare for the Worst
description: Axel and Bobbie Blobby skip out on Sarge's disaster-prep drills, leaving enough of a gap in the team's defenses for a crow to swoop in and snatch Sarge! Feeling responsible, Axel leads the team on a search-and-rescue mission.

title: Joyride
description: At a rummage sale with Uncle Andrew, Axel and Zoe must stop Madcap from turning her long-lost tank toy, Joyride, into an agent of mayhem!

title: Bringing Up Baby
description: Zoe leaves Axel in charge of the school project - watching over an infant simulator doll - but when MadCap brings the doll to life, Axel and the team must stop the baby without damaging it or risk getting a failing grade!

title: Freeze!
description: Axel and his team find themselves in a tough position after Ice Crusher makes it too cold for them to fight back at full speed.

title: The Scratch Pack
description: Axel and the team must run damage control after a loose spark of Minergy accidentally turns Zoe's old toys - a set of cute squishy kittens - into a pack of snarling beasts.

title: Side Kicked
description: Zoe builds her own battle suit in hopes of joining Axel's team. The only problem? She can't shrink! Hijinks ensue as a full-sized Zoe tries to assist Axel & co. in a battle against Pyrant and his army of mind-control drones.

title: Ride'em
description: One by one, the beaten up Power Players go and ask Slobot to fix them. What's going on?

title: Bobbie Not Blobby
description: Axel discovers that the culprit behind Bobbie Blobby's missing mech-suit is Masko, who only wanted to clean out its clogged clay cannons, but lets the suit fall into the hands (or tentacles) of Dr. Nautilus - intent on flooding the sewers!

title: The Banister of Victory
description: Action Axel organizes a jumping contest on the handrail of the stairs in the house!

title: Sarge in Charge
description: Axel and the team must rescue Sarge Charge from a solo mission in the backyard, which Orangutank has turned into his own personal heart of darkness.

title: Boo
description: Galileo thinks it's funny to play tricks on the Power Players, but how will they react?

title: Out of My Head
description: Axel must help Sarge and Bobbie learn to walk in each other's shoes - literally - after Luka unwittingly switches the toys' heads!

title: That Slobot Is No Bot of Mine
description: Axel and the team compete against themselves in tests of skill, strength, and stamina, but when SloBot gets belittled, he splits into three separate robots - each with their own evil personalities!

title: Masko
description: Action Axel tells us all about Masko.

title: A Great Hideout
description: Axel and the Power Players play hide and seek in the living room…it was Bobbie Blobbie's idea. But where is she hiding?

title: Porcupunk Rock
description: Madcap turns to Axel and his team for help after a sonic upgrade to Porcupunk threatens to bring down the house.

title: Winner Takes All
description: After months of training for Luchador Day, Axel needs Masko to coach him against a pair of uninvited competitors - Madcap and Dynamo!

title: Savage Axel
description: Bearbarian helps Axel get in touch with his wild side as Orangutank "liberates" nature from an apartment building - tossing potted plants of all sizes out the window and onto innocent bystanders below!

title: Party On
description: As Zoe preps Cleo LeBall's birthday party, Axel and the team run damage control against a jealous crasher - Princess SugarSalt, who has turned the decorations and gifts into instruments of chaos!

title: Joke's on You, Bro!
description: Axel and the team turn Galileo's camouflaging pranks around on him, convincing the gullible gecko that he's permanently invisible - to disastrous results!

title: Return of Thermometron 9000
description: During a brutal heatwave, Axel and his team must track down Thermometron 9000, stolen by Ice Crusher for two purposes - to keep his hockey rink from melting and to bait the good toys into a rematch!

title: Access Denied
description: When Axel and the team try to figure out what Sarge Charge's secret weapon is, they get ejected from the house by his newly upgraded security system and must fight their way back inside before Madcap does.

title: Madtrap
description: Madcap and Princess SugarSalt trap Axel and the team inside a Minergy-powered labyrinth that attacks them with their greatest fears, forcing them to work together and escape as a unit.

title: The Other Side
description: Axel must 'save' Bobbie Blobby after she defects to Madcap's team, tempted by Porcupunk and his assertion that she belongs with the bad toys.

title: Stretched Too Thin
description: After a new combo-move leaves Masko permanently limp, Axel and the team must help the fallen luchador get his stretch back.

title: The Thing in the Wall
description: When Axel and the team accuse Galileo of stealing their possessions, the lizard must hunt down the true culprit - a mysterious creature behind the wall - to prove his innocence.

title: Just Like Robots
description: Axel and the team find themselves bested by Madcap when the baddie uses their digital devices to track their every move in combat, forcing our heroes to act unpredictably.

title: For Elite Only
description: Sarge gets Action Axel ready for an elite mission...he's just not sure which mission!

title: Green with Envy
description: When the local news interviews Uncle Andrew about his toy inventing, an envious Galileo stages a play in the park with the help of Axel and the team, only to be interrupted by an equally envious Madcap - out to steal the spotlight for himself!

title: The Best Team
description: When Madcap and his minions crash a soapbox derby, the team must stop the baddies and help Axel - stuck in a car with Luka - cross the finish line!

title: Iced Out
description: Madcap's latest creation, the Ice Crusher, puts the whole city in a deep freeze, forcing Axel and the team to face him in a game of high-stakes hockey or risk slip-sliding into another ice age!

title: The Trojan Bear
description: When Axel opens a subscription gift-box he didn't even order, the team finds their ranks divided by a robotic bear - or Princess SugarSalt in disguise!

title: Knockout
description: Axel and the team juggle not waking Uncle Andrew from his nap and stopping Orangutank from stealing Andrew's latest invention: the Knockout Box!

title: Attack of Thermometron 9000
description: Axel must wrangle Galileo and Bobbie to shut down a rogue thermostat - improperly upgraded by Slobot - as it plunges the house into extreme hot and cold zones.

title: King Axel
description: After a screening of the King Arthur tale, Axel holds out his sword and declares himself king, but when Dynamo uses his magnetism to steal the weapon and bestow it upon Masko, it casts doubt among the team over who is the true leader.

title: Bearbarian
description: Action Axel tells us all about Bearbarian.

title: Grin and Bear It
description: When a toothache sends Axel to the dentist, the team must fight off Princess SugarSalt, who confuses Axel's new "crown" for the real thing.

title: On Your Toes
description: After a Porcupunk sighting, Axel leads a recon mission that slowly but surely proves to be a wild goose chase devised by Sarge, who's secretly pursuing a hobby that he's afraid to share with his teammates.

title: Emergency
description: Slobot arrives looking panicked while Sarge Charge is training: it's Axel!

title: Madcap
description: Action Axel and Galileo tell us all about...Madcap!

title: Galileo
description: Action Axel tells us all about Galileo.

title: Sarge Charge
description: Sarge Charge tells tales from the battlefield…from a toy's perspective!

title: Power Chef
description: The Power Players do some cooking…in their own special way!

title: Dodge City
description: Axel embraces the spirit of dodgeball to stop Madcap and Princess SugarSalt's battle over who is the better villain from spilling over into Zoe and Cleo's argument over who is the better coach!

title: Bring on the Bad Guys
description: Axel, Zoe, and the team confront Madcap and his minions as they terrorize a local supermarket.

title: The Dynamo Dynamic
description: Axel finds himself at the center of a disagreement between Sarge and Masko over what's more important in battle - the weapon or the one who wields it - after Dynamo bonds the trio together!

title: Unboxing Part 2
description: Axel discovers that he can transform into a toy and teams up with his new team of toys to stop Madcap from stealing a Minergy battery.

title: To Tame the Perilous Skies!
description: With Axel's drone-wing broken, the team must find another way to stop Madcap and his minions as they take to the skies in toy airplanes for an aerial assault on the city park.

title: Make Over
description: Bearbarian asks Slobot to dye his fur a different color.

title: Stuck on You
description: Tired of Axel and the team taking him for granted, Masko tries to get kidnapped and ends up stuck to Dynamo, who's less than enthused with his rubbery new sidekick.

title: Spies Like Us
description: Uncle Andrew warns Axel that his vintage "Agent Danger" action figure is off-limits, only to have the toy escape on its own! Axel and the team must return Danger to its rightful place before Uncle Andrew finds out.

title: Unboxing Part 1
description: Axel ventures into his uncle's strictly off-limits basement lab in hopes of fixing a broken toy and ends up unleashing living ones instead: the renegade Madcap and a whole team of superpowered toys dedicated to stopping him!

title: Bobbie Blobby
description: Action Axel tells us all about Bobbie Blobby.

title: All Trick No Treat
description: On Halloween, Axel gets too caught up in the scares and loses track of the fun - just in time for an infiltration by the worst trick 'r' treater of all, Madcap!

title: A Titans Showdown
description: The Power Players clash in Masko's ring... in a laughing contest!

title: Opposites Attract
description: Claiming he's good at heart, Dynamo convinces Axel and the team to help him find a battery that can power his centrifuge and free him from Madtrap's control - but Bobbie Blobby isn't buying the baddie's story.

title: Axel
description: Galileo tells us all about Axel. Or not!

title: Zoe
description: Action Axel tells us all about Zoe.

title: Friend Wars
description: Princess SugarSalt dupes Axel into hanging out with Cleo LeBall and usurps his role as team leader, forcing Zoe to step in and keep the toys together.

title: Thirst for Power
description: Axel and his toys deploy the Joyride in a "ship" to "ship" battle against Dr. Nautilus, who has punctured a water main to flood the sewers and established himself as "Admiral Nautilus."

title: Sand Trap
description: Axel and the team take to the desert dunes of a playground sandbox as Madcap attempts to unearth an army of Spy Lizards from the same line as Galileo!

title: Four Color Fallout
description: Axel, Galileo, and Sarge get Minergy-transported by Madcap into the pages of Axel's favorite comic book, the hero of which turns out not to be so cool after all.

title: From Below
description: Axel juggles looking after Luka and defending the house from Dr. Nautilus's latest abomination, a tentacle monster that attacks from every drain, pipe, and faucet in the building!

title: Gathering Dark
description: Axel must help Bearbarian overcome his secret fear of the dark to stop Dynamo from stealing his ride.

title: Beware of the Luka
description: Luka wants to borrow one of Axel's seemingly "inanimate" Power Players.

title: Countdown
description: Axel has to clean up the living room in time for his uncle's dinner party, but trying to do too much at once leaves him stuck as a toy with Orangutank on the loose and less than an hour until the guests arrive.

title: Bear-Knuckle Brawl
description: Axel must team up with Bearbarian to stop Madcap from transforming Luka's stuffed bear collection into an invincible army.

title: Slobot
description: Action Axel tells us all about Slobot.
